Privacy policy
Last update November 30th, 2016
Platform Inc. respects the privacy of its online visitors and users of its website, products and services. Platform Inc. recognizes the importance of protecting information collected from users and has adopted this privacy policy to inform users about how Platform Inc. gathers, stores, and uses information derived from their use of Platform Inc. products, services and online sites.
This policy is current as of its last revision date. However, please note that this policy may be amended from time to time to reflect changes and additions to the privacy policy. Please check back for the most current version before relying on any of the provisions in this privacy policy.
